headline: United States Foodservice Market Forecast Report 2025: A $1.97 Trillion Market by 2033, Driven by Rising Online Ordering, Convenience Trends, and Growth of QSRs and Upscale Dining Establishments
summary: The United States Foodservice Market is projected to expand from US$ 846 Billion in 2024 to US$ 1.97 trillion by 2033, driven by a CAGR of 9.85% from 2025 to 2033. Key growth factors include rising consumer demand for convenience, online food ordering, and a surge in quick-service and upscale dining venues.
